The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 New hairstyle for Beckham

Madrid: David Beckham is sporting a new platinum blond hairstyle as he prepares to bring down the curtain on his Real Madrid career before joining American club Los Angeles Galaxy in the summer. 

Beckham, who was uncharacteristically coy about showing off the look, has gone through a range of different hairstyles in his four years in Spain. (AFP) 




